{"tha-ap322:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap322:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap322:0.3":"Kumudamaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap322:1.1":"“Usabham pavaram viram, ","tha-ap322:1.2":"mahesim vijitavinam; ","tha-ap322:1.3":"Vipassinam mahaviram, ","tha-ap322:1.4":"abhijatamva kesarim. ","tha-ap322:2.1":"Rathiyam patipajjantam, ","tha-ap322:2.2":"ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap322:2.3":"Gahetva kumudam malam, ","tha-ap322:2.4":"buddhasettham samokirim. ","tha-ap322:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap322:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap322:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap322:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap322:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap322:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap322:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap322:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kumudamaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap322:6.1":"Kumudamaliyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap322:7.1":"Arakkhadayakavaggo battimsatimo. ","tha-ap322:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap322:9.1":"Arakkhado bhojanado, ","tha-ap322:9.2":"gatasanni padumiyo; ","tha-ap322:9.3":"Pupphasani santhaviko, ","tha-ap322:9.4":"saddasanni tiramsiyo; ","tha-ap322:9.5":"Kandaliko kumudi ca, ","tha-ap322:9.6":"sattapannasa gathakati. "}